{"tid":102330,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"物理撚來挑機吧!","createTime":"2017-01-31T14:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T15:44:42.000Z","uid":64262,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f7884dcf19710fc17adeefa679069d0f9e461fd4","tid":102330,"uid":64262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"認真試過問呢條問題,個prof 唔識答。<br />\n<br />\n一個斜坡上有一塊block, 個block 均速和下郁<br />\n求斜坡同block 對地球嘅Normal force<br />\n<br />\n1) 斜坡同地球有friction<br />\n<br />\n2) 斜坡同地球冇friction<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"96a6aef51fd9c9b26a1e810881b8c8020c8a6b8f","tid":102330,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"自己功課自己做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73d920a7ad271f5594331a6b0777b7221f43849","tid":102330,"uid":65351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"1 有。自己計 <br />\n<br />\n2 冇friction = 冇 normal force"},{"pid":"47bcd04e747a9455118aa1a373f0e29497450ecd","tid":102330,"uid":64262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:24:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1 有。自己計 <br />\n<br />\n2 冇friction = 冇 normal force</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你意思係兩個唔同?"},{"pid":"d7df10f08a369fc7aa8b0d6ad1006208a7099bf4","tid":102330,"uid":64349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:25:32.000Z","msg":"細到可以話無"},{"pid":"e0832ea6bdcd6e13b3f81e554e1eb413f205b7c6","tid":102330,"uid":64262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己功課自己做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有咁嘅功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2fc40286e23d234fdaa2212288eb325e5cbd3f","tid":102330,"uid":74465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:29:44.000Z","msg":"均速向下郁 即係net force=0 咁個normal force 就= W cos 