d":102330,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"你無比兩個物件mass<br />\nmass of block = m <br />\nmass of wedge = M<br />\n<br />\n(1) 當f夠大,wedge唔會郁<br />\nconsider m,M as a system<br />\nCOM moves with constant velocity so there is no horizontal or vertical COM acceleration <br />\nthere the net force on system = 0<br />\n<br />\nNormal force = (M+m)g<br />\n<br />\n(2) 無f<br />\nCOM horizontal speed = 0<br />\nCOM vertical speed = const<br />\nso the <br />\nnormal force = (m+M)g<br />\n<br />\nBoth are same <br />\n利申: 唔會錯"},{"pid":"7b9c930fe52223ca1e197ad890b0d4ede51f1687","tid":102330,"uid":64262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你無比兩個物件mass<br />\nmass of block = m <br />\nmass of wedge = M<br />\n<br />\n(1) 當f夠大,wedge唔會郁<br />\nconsider m,M as a system<br />\nCOM moves with constant velocity so there is no horizontal or vertical COM acceleration <br />\nthere the net force on system = 0<br />\n<br />\nNormal force = (M+m)g<br />\n<br />\n(2) 無f<br />\nCOM horizontal speed = 0<br />\nCOM vertical speed = const<br />\nso the <br />\nnormal force = (m+M)g<br />\n<br />\nBoth are same <br />\n利申: 唔會錯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae4d2e6bfaa3d21dd33c267d589f0fc85ad7f65","tid":102330,"uid":64262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:40:40.000Z","msg":"再問吓大神們, 如果斜坡冇咗friction,個Total N 係咪一樣?"},{"pid":"57ef9d75e11bae2d087f301608605b183ad77d98","tid":102330,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再問吓大神們, 如果斜坡冇咗friction,個Total N 係咪一樣?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nyou mean there is no friction between wedge and block?<br />\n<br />\nthere the block will accelerate<br />\n<br />\ntotal N changes"},{"pid":"f3bfb4447480aa281f8b06ee8c992acb58c6b54f","tid":102330,"uid":64262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>再問吓大神們, 如果斜坡冇咗friction,個Total N 係咪一樣?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nyou mean there is no friction between wedge and block?<br />\n<br />\nthere the block will accelerate<br />\n<br />\ntotal N changes</blockquote><br />\nIn terms of Newton 3rd law, 點解冇friction 同有friction會唔同?"},{"pid":"a7b2752b76783ec9ef498f56ed7a0bb8e6f636ed","tid":102330,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"on9,有冇 friction同 normal force有咁關係, 一個 horizontal一個 vertical"},{"pid":"cb0609088f035778f3890809c37eb9cc5fc7dccb","tid":102330,"uid":64262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9,有冇 friction同 normal force有咁關係, 一個 horizontal一個 vertical</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第二條呢?"},{"pid":"28e6d092379003924d90de8e173bd799790826e5","tid":102330,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再問吓大神們, 如果斜坡冇咗friction,個Total N 係咪一樣?</blockquote><br />\nnormal force會細左，細幾多同斜坡角度有關<br />\n利申AL physics攞d,非物理系"},{"pid":"c339a4ea2cbe7908d4cbe7518f44cacf7f9445e6","tid":102330,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/x19485IMG_20173149x82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fx19485IMG_20173149x82.jpg&h=1d70b9ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"643864c7807e39bf203909f8838d532d2781d833","tid":102330,"uid":64262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>再問吓大神們, 如果斜坡冇咗friction,個Total N 係咪一樣?</blockquote><br />\nnormal force會細左，細幾多同斜坡角度有關<br />\n利申AL physics攞d,非物理系</blockquote><br />\n第三條呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmo